## 🎯 PROJECT VISION



Transform SAGE from a simple terminal command wrapper into a **complete AI-powered development orchestration platform** with:



- ✅ **Automatic error fixing** with ML-based confidence scoring

- ✅ **Multi-agent coordination** for parallel task execution  

- ✅ **Workflow automation** with YAML-based pipelines

- ✅ **Real-time monitoring** via REST API dashboard

- ✅ **MCP integration** for MCP-compatible client

- ✅ **ML-based failure prediction** before execution

- ✅ **Natural language interface** for intuitive commands

- ✅ **Cross-project intelligence** sharing patterns globally



---



## 🚀 QUICK START



### Installation



```bash

# Clone repository

git clone https://github.com/PsYcGoD/sage.git

cd sage



# Install in development mode

python -m pip install -e .



# Run from source

cd src

python -m sage --version

```



### First Commands



```bash

# Run a command through SAGE

cd src && python -m sage run -- python test.py



# Get auto-fix suggestion

cd src && python -m sage fix



# Apply the fix

cd src && python -m sage fix --apply



# List all agents

cd src && python -m sage agents list



# Run a workflow

cd src && python -m sage workflow run test



# Start dashboard

cd src && python -m sage dashboard start



# Install MCP server

cd src && python -m sage mcp install

```



