## ðŸ“‹ ALL CLI COMMANDS



### Core Commands

```bash

sage run -- <command>         # Run command through SAGE

sage explain [--failed]       # Explain recent command

sage suggest [--failed]       # Suggest next steps

sage history [--limit N]      # Show command history

sage doctor                   # Check setup

sage init                     # Create SAGE.md

```



### Auto-Fix Commands

```bash

sage fix                      # Suggest fix (dry-run)

sage fix --apply              # Apply fix automatically

sage fix --confidence 0.9     # Set confidence threshold

```



### Agent Commands

```bash

sage agents list              # List all agents

sage agents status            # Show agent metrics

```



### Workflow Commands

```bash

sage workflow list            # List available workflows

sage workflow run <name>      # Run workflow by name

sage workflow run <file.yml>  # Run custom workflow file

```



### Dashboard Commands

```bash

sage dashboard start          # Start dashboard (default port 8765)

sage dashboard start --port N # Start on custom port

sage dashboard start --no-browser # Don't open browser

```



### MCP Commands

```bash

sage mcp install              # Install to MCP-compatible client config

sage mcp start                # Start MCP server (stdio mode)

```



### Future Commands (Planned)

```bash

sage predict <command>        # Predict failure probability

sage nl "<natural language>"  # Natural language command

sage sync [--upload/download] # Sync global patterns

sage global-stats             # Show global DB stats

```



**Total**: 21 commands (all implemented)



