## ðŸ’» DEVELOPMENT SETUP



### Requirements



- Python 3.10+

- SQLite 3 (included with Python)

- Optional: FastAPI, uvicorn (for dashboard)

- Optional: PyYAML (for workflows)



### Installation



```bash

# Clone repository

git clone https://github.com/PsYcGoD/sage.git

cd sage



# Install in development mode

python -m pip install -e .



# Install optional dependencies

pip install pyyaml                    # For workflows

pip install fastapi uvicorn[standard] # For dashboard

```



### Database Location



```bash

# View database path

cd src && python -m sage doctor



# Inspect database

sqlite3 %LOCALAPPDATA%\SAGE\sage.db  # Windows

sqlite3 ~/.sage/sage.db              # Unix



# Show tables

.tables



# Query data

SELECT * FROM runs ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT * FROM agents;

SELECT * FROM fixes;

```



### Development Commands



```bash

# Run from source

cd src

python -m sage --version



# Test CLI

python -m sage run -- echo "Hello SAGE"

python -m sage explain

python -m sage agents list



# Test dashboard

python -m sage dashboard start



# Test MCP

python -m sage mcp install

```



