## ðŸš¢ DEPLOYMENT



### Local Development

```bash

# Run from source

cd src && python -m sage <command>

```



### System-Wide Installation

```bash

# Install package

python -m pip install -e .



# Add to PATH (Windows)

# Add Python\Scripts to PATH environment variable



# Add to PATH (Unix)

echo 'export PATH="$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.bashrc

```



### Docker Deployment

```dockerfile

FROM python:3.10-slim



WORKDIR /app

COPY . .



RUN pip install -e .



# Run dashboard

CMD ["python", "-m", "sage.dashboard.server"]

```



### CI/CD Integration

```yaml

# .github/workflows/sage.yml

name: SAGE CI



on: [push]



jobs:

  test:

    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:

      - uses: actions/checkout@v2

      - uses: actions/setup-python@v2

        with:

          python-version: '3.10'

      - run: pip install -e .

      - run: cd src && python -m sage workflow run ci

```



